---
title: Crunchy Italian Sheet-Pan Chicken 2x the delicious portions!
description: Having family or friends over? This extra-generous, Italian-inspired dinner is perfect for a crowd! All you have to do is boil potatoes, pop chicken and green beans in the oven, and wait for the deliciousness. The best part (besides digging in)? Fewer pots and pans means more time enjoying your people.  *This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.*

***The image pictured is similar to our Crunchy Italian Sheet-Pan Chicken—but not exact! As always, please consult the ingredients list for more detailed recipe information and allergens.***
